{
  "video_id": "G244Q4AGJ7U",
  "title": "When is water safe to drink? - Mia Nacamulli",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 8640.0,
      "end_time": 10611.0,
      "text": "Take a look at the water in this glass."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10611.0,
      "end_time": 14355.0,
      "text": "Refreshing, hydrating, and invaluable to your survival."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14355.0,
      "end_time": 15929.0,
      "text": "Before you take a sip, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 15929.0,
      "end_time": 20926.0,
      "text": "how do you know that the water inside is free from disease-causing organisms"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20926.0,
      "end_time": 22589.0,
      "text": "and pollutants?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22589.0,
      "end_time": 25590.0,
      "text": "One out of ten people in the world can't actually be sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25591.0,
      "end_time": 28431.0,
      "text": "that their water is clean  and safe to drink."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28431.0,
      "end_time": 31386.0,
      "text": "Why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31386.0,
      "end_time": 32806.0,
      "text": "Inadequate sanitation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32806.0,
      "end_time": 34916.0,
      "text": "poor protection of drinking water sources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34916.0,
      "end_time": 36654.0,
      "text": "and improper hygiene"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36655.0,
      "end_time": 40377.0,
      "text": "often lead to sewage and feces-contaminated water"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40377.0,
      "end_time": 43198.0,
      "text": "That's the ideal breeding ground for dangerous bacteria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43198.0,
      "end_time": 44258.0,
      "text": "viruses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44258.0,
      "end_time": 45989.0,
      "text": "and parasites."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 45989.0,
      "end_time": 49770.0,
      "text": "And the effects of these pathogens are staggering."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 49780.0,
      "end_time": 52904.0,
      "text": "Diarrheal disease from unsafe water is one of the leading causes of death"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52904.0,
      "end_time": 56187.0,
      "text": "around the world for children under five."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56187.0,
      "end_time": 58587.0,
      "text": "And according to a U.N. report from 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58588.0,
      "end_time": 65739.0,
      "text": "microbial water-borne illnesses killed more people per year than war."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65739.0,
      "end_time": 69808.0,
      "text": "Proper treatment processes, though, can address these threats."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69808.0,
      "end_time": 71538.0,
      "text": "They usually have three parts:"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71538.0,
      "end_time": 72607.0,
      "text": "sedimentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72607.0,
      "end_time": 73739.0,
      "text": "filtration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73739.0,
      "end_time": 75329.0,
      "text": "and disinfection."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75329.0,
      "end_time": 77857.0,
      "text": "Once water has been collected in a treatment facility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77857.0,
      "end_time": 79598.0,
      "text": "it's ready for cleaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79598.0,
      "end_time": 83139.0,
      "text": "The first step, sedimentation, just takes time."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83139.0,
      "end_time": 88339.0,
      "text": "The water sits undisturbed, allowing heavier particles to sink to the bottom."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88339.0,
      "end_time": 91390.0,
      "text": "Often, though, particles  are just too small"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91400.0,
      "end_time": 93244.0,
      "text": "to be removed by sedimentation alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93244.0,
      "end_time": 95189.0,
      "text": "and need to be filtered."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95189.0,
      "end_time": 98378.0,
      "text": "Gravity pulls the water downward through layers of sand"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98379.0,
      "end_time": 101250.0,
      "text": "that catch leftover particles  in their pores,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101250.0,
      "end_time": 103750.0,
      "text": "prepping the water  for its final treatment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103750.0,
      "end_time": 105811.0,
      "text": "a dose of disinfectant."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105811.0,
      "end_time": 109870.0,
      "text": "Chemicals, primarily forms  of chlorine and ozone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109870.0,
      "end_time": 111750.0,
      "text": "are mixed in to kill off any pathogens"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111750.0,
      "end_time": 115279.0,
      "text": "and to disinfect pipes and storage systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115279.0,
      "end_time": 119112.0,
      "text": "Chlorine is highly effective in destroying water's living organisms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 119112.0,
      "end_time": 121482.0,
      "text": "but its use remains government-regulated"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 121482.0,
      "end_time": 124801.0,
      "text": "because it has potentially harmful chemical byproducts."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 124801.0,
      "end_time": 129390.0,
      "text": "And if an imbalance of chlorine occurs during the disinfection process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129389.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132900.0,
      "text": "it can trigger other chemical reactions."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 132910.0,
      "end_time": 134603.0,
      "text": "For example,  levels of chlorine byproducts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134603.0,
      "end_time": 138881.0,
      "text": "like trihalomethanes, could skyrocket, leading to pipe corrosion"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 138881.0,
      "end_time": 145492.0,
      "text": "and the release of iron, copper, and lead into drinking water."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145492.0,
      "end_time": 147892.0,
      "text": "Water contamination from these and other sources"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 147892.0,
      "end_time": 149420.0,
      "text": "including leaching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149420.0,
      "end_time": 150392.0,
      "text": "chemical spills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150392.0,
      "end_time": 151591.0,
      "text": "and runoffs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 151592.0,
      "end_time": 153814.0,
      "text": "has been linked  to long-term health effects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 153814.0,
      "end_time": 154620.0,
      "text": "like cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 154620.0,
      "end_time": 157343.0,
      "text": "cardiovascular and neurological diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 157343.0,
      "end_time": 159493.0,
      "text": "and miscarriage."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 159493.0,
      "end_time": 161704.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, analyzing the exact risks"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 161704.0,
      "end_time": 164010.0,
      "text": "of chemically contaminated  water is difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 164010.0,
      "end_time": 167651.0,
      "text": "So while it's clear that disinfectants make us safer"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 167651.0,
      "end_time": 169954.0,
      "text": "by removing disease-causing pathogens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 169954.0,
      "end_time": 172234.0,
      "text": "experts have yet  to determine the full scope"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 172234.0,
      "end_time": 175350.0,
      "text": "of how the chemical cocktail  in our drinking water"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 175350.0,
      "end_time": 178130.0,
      "text": "really impacts human health."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 178130.0,
      "end_time": 181566.0,
      "text": "So how can you tell whether the water you have access to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 181566.0,
      "end_time": 183585.0,
      "text": "whether from a tap or otherwise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 183585.0,
      "end_time": 185365.0,
      "text": "is drinkable?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 185365.0,
      "end_time": 187185.0,
      "text": "Firstly, too much turbidity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 187185.0,
      "end_time": 188935.0,
      "text": "trace organic compounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 188935.0,
      "end_time": 193776.0,
      "text": "or high-density heavy metals like arsenic, chromium, or lead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 193776.0,
      "end_time": 197215.0,
      "text": "mean that the water  is unsuitable for consumption."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 197215.0,
      "end_time": 199805.0,
      "text": "A lot of contaminants,  like lead or arsenic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 199805.0,
      "end_time": 201867.0,
      "text": "won't be obvious without tests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 201867.0,
      "end_time": 203804.0,
      "text": "but some clues, like cloudiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 203805.0,
      "end_time": 205816.0,
      "text": "brown or yellow coloration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 205816.0,
      "end_time": 207730.0,
      "text": "a foul odor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 207730.0,
      "end_time": 209687.0,
      "text": "or an excessive chlorine smell"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 209687.0,
      "end_time": 212518.0,
      "text": "can indicate the need to investigate further."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 212518.0,
      "end_time": 214666.0,
      "text": "Water testing kits can go a step further"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 214666.0,
      "end_time": 219887.0,
      "text": "and confirm the presence of many different contaminants and chemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 219887.0,
      "end_time": 221520.0,
      "text": "With many types of contamination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 221520.0,
      "end_time": 225941.0,
      "text": "there are ways of treating water where  it's used instead of close to its source."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 225941.0,
      "end_time": 230127.0,
      "text": "Point-of-use treatment has actually been around for thousands of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 230127.0,
      "end_time": 235598.0,
      "text": "Ancient Egyptians boiled away many organic contaminants with the sun's heat."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 235598.0,
      "end_time": 238522.0,
      "text": "And in Ancient Greece, Hippocrates designed a bag"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 238522.0,
      "end_time": 242286.0,
      "text": "that trapped bad tasting  sediments from water."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 242287.0,
      "end_time": 245857.0,
      "text": "Today, point-of-use processes usually involve ionization"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 245857.0,
      "end_time": 247579.0,
      "text": "to lower mineral content."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 247579.0,
      "end_time": 250389.0,
      "text": "They also use adsorption filtration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 250389.0,
      "end_time": 253347.0,
      "text": "where a porous material called activated carbon"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 253347.0,
      "end_time": 257870.0,
      "text": "strains the water to remove contaminants and chemical byproducts."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 257870.0,
      "end_time": 260819.0,
      "text": "While it's not always an effective long-term solution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 260819.00000000003,
      "end_time": 265499.0,
      "text": "point-of-use treatment is portable, easy to install, and adaptable."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 265499.0,
      "end_time": 268698.0,
      "text": "And in regions where large-scale systems are unavailable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 268698.0,
      "end_time": 272131.0,
      "text": "or where water has been contaminated further along its journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 272131.0,
      "end_time": 276568.0,
      "text": "these systems can mean the difference between life and death."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 276569.0,
      "end_time": 280990.0,
      "text": "Clean water remains a precious and often scarce commodity."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 280990.0,
      "end_time": 284982.0,
      "text": "There are nearly 800 million of us who still don't have regular access to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 284982.0,
      "end_time": 288610.0,
      "text": "The good news is that continued developments in water treatment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 288610.0,
      "end_time": 290301.0,
      "text": "both on a large and small scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 290301.0,
      "end_time": 292811.0,
      "text": "can alleviate a lot of unsafe conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 292811.0,
      "end_time": 295111.0,
      "text": "Implementing proper systems where they're needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 295111.0,
      "end_time": 298489.0,
      "text": "and paying careful attention to the ones already in place"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 298489.0,
      "end_time": 301869.0,
      "text": "will fulfill one of the most basic of our human needs."
    }
  ]
}